        { "action": "highlight", "target": "hidden_layer_summary", "at": "4.3s", "duration": "2.0s", "color": "accent", "style": "glow" },
        { "action": "draw", "target": "overview_hidden_to_out", "at": "6.7s", "duration": "1.0s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "prediction_summary", "at": "6.9s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "highlight", "target": "prediction_summary", "at": "8.2s", "duration": "2.0s", "color": "success", "style": "glow" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "formula_row", "at": "10.6s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "formula_sum", "at": "10.8s", "duration": "0.6s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "formula_bias", "at": "11.3s", "duration": "0.6s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "formula_relu", "at": "11.8s", "duration": "0.6s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "formula_output", "at": "12.3s", "duration": "0.6s" },
        { "action": "highlight", "target": "step_overview", "at": "0s", "duration": "14.6s", "color": "accent", "style": "glow" },
        { "action": "scale", "target": "step_overview", "at": "0.1s", "duration": "0.8s", "scale_factor": 1.12 }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "hidden_sum",
      "duration": "18s",
      "template": "one-column",
      "auto_visible": false,
      "narration": "Now let's slow down and look at why this weighted sum exists. Each weight tells the neuron how strongly to listen to one input. The multiplication scales that input's influence, and the sign tells us whether it supports or opposes the neuron firing. Then we add the contributions together because the neuron is pooling evidence from all of its incoming inputs.",
      "objects": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "hidden_sum_title",
          "content": "1. Compute One Hidden Weighted Sum",
          "style": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "group",
          "id": "hidden_sum_stack",
          "visible": true,
          "layout": { "type": "stack", "direction": "vertical", "gap": "large", "align": "center" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "group",
              "id": "term_row",
              "visible": true,
              "layout": { "type": "flow", "direction": "horizontal", "gap": "large", "align": "center" },
              "children": [
                { "type": "box", "id": "term_1", "content": "0.70 x 0.50 = 0.35" },
                { "type": "box", "id": "term_2", "content": "-0.40 x -0.30 = 0.12" }
              ]
            },
            { "type": "box", "id": "partial_sum", "content": "0.35 + 0.12 = 0.47" },
            {
              "type": "group",
              "id": "weight_note_row",
              "layout": { "type": "flow", "direction": "horizontal", "gap": "medium", "align": "center" },
              "children": [
                { "type": "token", "id": "term_1_label", "content": "x1 contributes evidence to h1" },
                { "type": "token", "id": "term_2_label", "content": "x2 contributes evidence to h1" }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        { "type": "connector", "id": "term_1_to_sum", "from": "term_1", "to": "partial_sum" },
        { "type": "connector", "id": "term_2_to_sum", "from": "term_2", "to": "partial_sum" }
      ],
      "animations": [
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "hidden_sum_title", "at": "0s", "duration": "0.7s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "term_1", "at": "0.9s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "highlight", "target": "term_1", "at": "1.9s", "duration": "1.6s", "color": "accent", "style": "glow" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "term_2", "at": "4.3s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "highlight", "target": "term_2", "at": "5.3s", "duration": "1.6s", "color": "accent", "style": "glow" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "weight_note_row", "at": "7.6s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "term_1_label", "at": "7.8s", "duration": "0.6s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "term_2_label", "at": "8.3s", "duration": "0.6s" },
        { "action": "draw", "target": "term_1_to_sum", "at": "10.2s", "duration": "0.9s" },
        { "action": "draw", "target": "term_2_to_sum", "at": "10.7s", "duration": "0.9s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "partial_sum", "at": "11.3s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "highlight", "target": "partial_sum", "at": "12.6s", "duration": "2.0s", "color": "success", "style": "glow" },
        { "action": "highlight", "target": "step_hidden_sum", "at": "0s", "duration": "16.6s", "color": "accent", "style": "glow" },
        { "action": "scale", "target": "step_hidden_sum", "at": "0.1s", "duration": "0.8s", "scale_factor": 1.12 }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "add_bias",
      "duration": "18s",
      "template": "one-column",
      "auto_visible": false,
      "narration": "The bias is not just a random extra number. It lets the neuron shift its baseline before the activation function sees the result, which means it controls how easy or hard it is for that neuron to turn on. Here the weighted evidence is zero point four seven, the bias nudges it upward by zero point one zero, and that moves the pre-activation to zero point five seven.",
      "objects": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "bias_title",
          "content": "2. Add the Bias Term",
          "style": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "group",
          "id": "bias_stack",
          "visible": true,
          "layout": { "type": "stack", "direction": "vertical", "gap": "large", "align": "center" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "group",
              "id": "bias_inputs_row",
              "visible": true,
              "layout": { "type": "flow", "direction": "horizontal", "gap": "large", "align": "center" },
              "children": [
                { "type": "box", "id": "partial_sum", "content": "0.35 + 0.12 = 0.47" },
                { "type": "box", "id": "bias_value", "content": "bias = +0.10" }
              ]
            },
            { "type": "box", "id": "biased_total", "content": "0.47 + 0.10 = 0.57" },
            { "type": "box", "id": "z1_value", "content": "z1 = 0.57" },
            { "type": "token", "id": "bias_note", "content": "bias shifts the neuron's turn-on threshold" }
          ]
        },
        { "type": "connector", "id": "sum_to_biased_total", "from": "partial_sum", "to": "biased_total" },
        { "type": "connector", "id": "bias_to_biased_total", "from": "bias_value", "to": "biased_total" },
        { "type": "connector", "id": "biased_total_to_z1", "from": "biased_total", "to": "z1_value" }
      ],
      "animations": [
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "bias_title", "at": "0s", "duration": "0.7s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "partial_sum", "at": "0.9s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "bias_value", "at": "3.4s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "highlight", "target": "bias_value", "at": "4.5s", "duration": "1.5s", "color": "accent", "style": "glow" },
        { "action": "draw", "target": "sum_to_biased_total", "at": "7.2s", "duration": "0.9s" },
        { "action": "draw", "target": "bias_to_biased_total", "at": "7.7s", "duration": "0.9s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "biased_total", "at": "8.3s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "highlight", "target": "biased_total", "at": "9.6s", "duration": "1.8s", "color": "accent", "style": "glow" },
        { "action": "draw", "target": "biased_total_to_z1", "at": "12.0s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "z1_value", "at": "12.4s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "highlight", "target": "z1_value", "at": "13.7s", "duration": "1.8s", "color": "success", "style": "glow" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "bias_note", "at": "15.0s", "duration": "0.7s" },
        { "action": "highlight", "target": "step_bias", "at": "0s", "duration": "16.6s", "color": "accent", "style": "glow" },
        { "action": "scale", "target": "step_bias", "at": "0.1s", "duration": "0.8s", "scale_factor": 1.12 }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "relu",
      "duration": "19s",
      "template": "one-column",
      "auto_visible": false,
      "narration": "ReLU matters because it is what keeps the whole network from collapsing into one big linear equation. Its rule is simple: keep positive evidence, and clip negative values to zero. That introduces nonlinearity, which is what lets deeper networks model more interesting patterns. In this example h one survives because it is positive, while h two gets shut off because its pre-activation is negative.",
      "objects": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "relu_title",
          "content": "3. Apply ReLU to Hidden Neurons",
          "style": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "group",
          "id": "relu_row",
          "visible": true,
          "layout": { "type": "flow", "direction": "horizontal", "gap": "large", "align": "center" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "group",
              "id": "positive_lane",
              "visible": true,
              "layout": { "type": "stack", "direction": "vertical", "gap": "medium", "align": "center" },
              "children": [
                { "type": "box", "id": "z1_value", "content": "z1 = 0.57" },
                { "type": "box", "id": "relu_1", "content": "ReLU" },
                { "type": "box", "id": "h1_act", "content": "h1 = 0.57" }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "group",
              "id": "negative_lane",
              "visible": true,
              "layout": { "type": "stack", "direction": "vertical", "gap": "medium", "align": "center" },
              "children": [
                { "type": "box", "id": "z2_value", "content": "z2 = -0.56" },
                { "type": "box", "id": "relu_2", "content": "ReLU" },
                { "type": "box", "id": "h2_act", "content": "h2 = 0.00" }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "group",
              "id": "relu_note_row",
              "layout": { "type": "flow", "direction": "horizontal", "gap": "medium", "align": "center" },
              "children": [
                { "type": "token", "id": "relu_note_positive", "content": "positive values stay" },
                { "type": "token", "id": "relu_note_negative", "content": "negative values become 0" },
                { "type": "token", "id": "relu_note_nonlinear", "content": "this adds nonlinearity" }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        { "type": "connector", "id": "z1_to_relu", "from": "z1_value", "to": "relu_1" },
        { "type": "connector", "id": "relu_to_h1", "from": "relu_1", "to": "h1_act" },
        { "type": "connector", "id": "z2_to_relu", "from": "z2_value", "to": "relu_2" },
        { "type": "connector", "id": "relu_to_h2", "from": "relu_2", "to": "h2_act" }
      ],
      "animations": [
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "relu_title", "at": "0s", "duration": "0.7s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "relu_1", "at": "1.6s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "draw", "target": "z1_to_relu", "at": "2.3s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "draw", "target": "relu_to_h1", "at": "3.3s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "h1_act", "at": "3.7s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "highlight", "target": "h1_act", "at": "4.8s", "duration": "1.8s", "color": "success", "style": "glow" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "z2_value", "at": "7.5s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "relu_2", "at": "8.6s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "draw", "target": "z2_to_relu", "at": "9.3s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "draw", "target": "relu_to_h2", "at": "10.3s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "h2_act", "at": "10.7s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "highlight", "target": "h2_act", "at": "11.8s", "duration": "1.8s", "color": "accent", "style": "glow" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "relu_note_row", "at": "14.3s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "relu_note_positive", "at": "14.5s", "duration": "0.6s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "relu_note_negative", "at": "15.0s", "duration": "0.6s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "relu_note_nonlinear", "at": "15.5s", "duration": "0.6s" },
        { "action": "highlight", "target": "step_relu", "at": "0s", "duration": "17.6s", "color": "accent", "style": "glow" },
        { "action": "scale", "target": "step_relu", "at": "0.1s", "duration": "0.8s", "scale_factor": 1.12 }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "output_logit_scene",
      "duration": "20s",
      "template": "one-column",
      "auto_visible": false,
      "narration": "Now the hidden layer hands its features to the output neuron. This is a different neuron, so it uses its own output weights and its own output bias. The purpose of this step is to compress everything the hidden layer discovered into one score for the positive class. H one contributes strongly here, h two contributes nothing because ReLU already shut it off, and then the output bias shifts that combined score into the logit we will convert into a probability.",
      "objects": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "output_title",
          "content": "4. Build the Output Logit",
          "style": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "group",
          "id": "output_stack",
          "visible": true,
          "layout": { "type": "stack", "direction": "vertical", "gap": "large", "align": "center" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "group",
              "id": "output_activation_row",
              "visible": true,
              "layout": { "type": "flow", "direction": "horizontal", "gap": "large", "align": "center" },
              "children": [
                { "type": "box", "id": "h1_act", "content": "h1 = 0.57" },
                { "type": "box", "id": "h2_act", "content": "h2 = 0.00" }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "group",
              "id": "output_term_row",
              "visible": true,
              "layout": { "type": "flow", "direction": "horizontal", "gap": "large", "align": "center" },
              "children": [
                { "type": "box", "id": "out_term_1", "content": "h1 x w_out1 = 0.57 x 1.20 = 0.684" },
                { "type": "box", "id": "out_term_2", "content": "h2 x w_out2 = 0.00 x -0.70 = 0.000" }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "group",
              "id": "output_result_row",
              "visible": true,
              "layout": { "type": "stack", "direction": "vertical", "gap": "large", "align": "center" },
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "group",
                  "id": "output_merge_row",
                  "visible": true,
                  "layout": { "type": "flow", "direction": "horizontal", "gap": "large", "align": "center" },
                  "children": [
                    { "type": "box", "id": "output_partial", "content": "weighted sum = 0.684 + 0.000 = 0.684" },
                    { "type": "box", "id": "output_bias", "content": "output bias b_out = +0.05" }
                  ]
                },
                { "type": "box", "id": "output_total", "content": "logit = 0.684 + 0.05 = 0.734" },
                { "type": "box", "id": "output_logit", "content": "logit = 0.734" },
                { "type": "token", "id": "output_note", "content": "the output neuron has its own weights and bias" }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        { "type": "connector", "id": "h1_to_out_term_1", "from": "h1_act", "to": "out_term_1" },
        { "type": "connector", "id": "h2_to_out_term_2", "from": "h2_act", "to": "out_term_2" },
        { "type": "connector", "id": "out_term_1_to_partial", "from": "out_term_1", "to": "output_partial" },
        { "type": "connector", "id": "out_term_2_to_partial", "from": "out_term_2", "to": "output_partial" },
        { "type": "connector", "id": "partial_to_output_total", "from": "output_partial", "to": "output_total" },
        { "type": "connector", "id": "bias_to_output_total", "from": "output_bias", "to": "output_total" },
        { "type": "connector", "id": "output_total_to_logit", "from": "output_total", "to": "output_logit" }
      ],
      "animations": [
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "output_title", "at": "0s", "duration": "0.7s" },
        { "action": "highlight", "target": "h1_act", "at": "1.0s", "duration": "1.6s", "color": "success", "style": "glow" },
        { "action": "draw", "target": "h1_to_out_term_1", "at": "2.7s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "out_term_1", "at": "3.0s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "highlight", "target": "h2_act", "at": "5.0s", "duration": "1.6s", "color": "accent", "style": "glow" },
        { "action": "draw", "target": "h2_to_out_term_2", "at": "6.7s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "out_term_2", "at": "7.0s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "draw", "target": "out_term_1_to_partial", "at": "9.0s", "duration": "0.9s" },
        { "action": "draw", "target": "out_term_2_to_partial", "at": "9.5s", "duration": "0.9s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "output_partial", "at": "10.1s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "highlight", "target": "output_partial", "at": "11.3s", "duration": "1.6s", "color": "accent", "style": "glow" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "output_bias", "at": "13.0s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "draw", "target": "partial_to_output_total", "at": "14.2s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "draw", "target": "bias_to_output_total", "at": "14.7s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "output_total", "at": "15.2s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "draw", "target": "output_total_to_logit", "at": "16.5s", "duration": "0.8s" },
        { "action": "fade-in", "target": "output_logit", "at": "16.9s", "duration": "0.8s" },
